Additionally, the paper may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories as these fields are closely related to computer vision. The use of adaptive techniques in the proposed method may also suggest the involvement of neural networks and machine learning. The multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category may also be relevant as the paper deals with image analysis and processing. Finally, the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category may also be relevant as the paper involves the use of neural networks.
